Question: Join employees and departments to list staff names and their department codes for the 'Engineering' division.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "employees", "columns": ["employees.first_name", "employees.last_name", "departments.code"], "where": "employees.dept_id = departments.id AND departments.name = 'Engineering'", "limit": 30 }
Response: { "rows": [{"first_name": "Alan", "last_name": "Turing", "code": "ENG-01"}, {"first_name": "Grace", "last_name": "Hopper", "code": "ENG-02"}, {"first_name": "Linus", "last_name": "Torvalds", "code": "ENG-03"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 19 }
