Question: Select event titles and venue capacities by joining events and venues for concerts scheduled in June.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "events", "columns": ["events.title", "venues.capacity"], "where": "events.venue_id = venues.id AND events.event_type = 'Concert' AND events.date LIKE '2024-06-%'", "limit": 15 }
Response: { "rows": [{"title": "Summer Jazz Fest", "capacity": 5000}, {"title": "Rock Night Live", "capacity": 12000}, {"title": "Indie Showcase", "capacity": 800}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 23 }
