Question: Retrieve book titles and author names by joining books and authors where the genre is 'Science Fiction'.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "books", "columns": ["books.title", "authors.name"], "where": "books.author_id = authors.id AND books.genre = 'Science Fiction'", "limit": 20 }
Response: { "rows": [{"title": "Star Voyager", "name": "Isaac Asimov"}, {"title": "Neuromancer", "name": "William Gibson"}, {"title": "Dune", "name": "Frank Herbert"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 16 }
