Question: Join patients and doctors to find the diagnosis and appointment date for patient ID 772.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "patients", "columns": ["appointments.diagnosis", "appointments.date"], "where": "patients.id = appointments.patient_id AND patients.id = 772", "limit": 1 }
Response: { "rows": [{"diagnosis": "Seasonal Allergies", "date": "2024-03-14"}], "count": 1, "query_ms": 11 }
