Question: List restaurant names and cuisine types by joining restaurants and menus where the average rating is above 4.5.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "restaurants", "columns": ["restaurants.name", "menus.cuisine_type"], "where": "restaurants.menu_id = menus.id AND restaurants.rating > 4.5", "limit": 10 }
Response: { "rows": [{"name": "Le Petit Bistro", "cuisine_type": "French"}, {"name": "Sakura Sushi", "cuisine_type": "Japanese"}, {"name": "Taco Fiesta", "cuisine_type": "Mexican"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 20 }
